text: Locate the structure that is shrouded in thick smoke or fog, with its dark outline partly hidden but some of its features faintly visible through the mist.
Find the edifice whose dark form is partially concealed by heavy smoke or fog, with faint outlines showing through the obscurity.
Spot the building whose silhouette is dark and partially hidden by dense fog or smoke, with faint structural lines peeking through the murkiness.
